updateGradient

public void updateGradient(int parentDepth,
                           int depth,
                           int typeTables,
                           int customers,
                           int tables,
                           double pp,
                           double discount,
                           double multFactor)
Adds a factor to discount gradient. Method assumes that information is provided as you go UP the tree.

Parameters:
parentDepth - parent depth
depth - current depth
typeTables - number of tables of type inserted
customers - number of total customers in node
tables - number of total tables in node
pp - predictive probability of type in parent node
discount - discount in node
multFactor - factor by which to down-weight gradient update

stepDiscounts

Using gradient information, step the discounts. Then clears gradient information.

Parameters:
eps - governs step size
p - predictive probability of type prior to insertion into the model
